677
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,050
What, all the debts came due at once?

678
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:48,530
Yeah, that's why he...

679
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,690
Come on, stop it!

680
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,460
Took advantage of you?

681
