704
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:42,490
Does that

705
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:44,940
make sense?

706
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:01,980
Ma'am,

707
00:38:03,590 --> 00:38:04,940
are you saying

708
00:38:05,710 --> 00:38:07,340
