727
00:39:04,110 --> 00:39:04,690
It's all on record...

728
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:05,650
Qiao Zhenxing is dead.

729
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:06,570
Did you know that?

730
00:39:07,150 --> 00:39:08,570
Happened the same day as your hearing.

731
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:12,420
How would I know

732
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:14,050
in here?

733
00:39:16,230 --> 00:39:16,740
Wan Hai,

734
00:39:17,150 --> 00:39:19,340
this case just keeps getting bigger,

