00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:20,900
and the fallout is growing too.

736
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:22,740
It's no longer just

737
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:24,530
a local anti-gang case,

738
00:39:25,030 --> 00:39:26,210
and it's not something

739
00:39:26,230 --> 00:39:27,690
you can handle on your own.

740
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:32,530
If there's anything else
you need to say,

741
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:34,130
