00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:37,050
You have to fight for your rights,

743
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:39,820
and for your chance.

744
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:49,260
Wan Hai,

745
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:52,090
I don't know what you're so afraid of.

746
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:55,780
If the freight hub was yours,

747
00:39:56,190 --> 00:39:57,490
and so was the club,

748
00:39:57,630 --> 00:39:58,900
you should stand up

